## How to verify on your machine

```bash
canifinetune bench \
  --model "{{ model_id }}" \
  --method {{ method }} \
  --seq-len {{ seq_len }} \
  --micro-batch-size {{ micro_batch_size }} \
  --lora-rank {{ lora_rank }} \
  --steps 3
```
